title: Bobby Gets Medical Advice From Listener + Eddie Takes Yellow Jacket Energy Pills + Lunchbox Attempts To Get Strangers To Cheer For Him

description:
Bobby talks to a nurse on the air about some red bumps that have shown up on his arms. Eddie takes 4 Yellow Jacket energy pills live on the air. Also, Lunchbox attempts to get crowds to cheer for him with random life announcements!
